{"id": "1427282423749541928", "channel_id": "1427282423749541928", "type": 0, "author_id": "688380814370930815", "author_name": "lalalanz.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Good evening, I am fairly new, about in game 1 week old and may I ask questions about...\n\n1. Is there a need to build more than 1 team for the game?\n2. Standard Pulls - Build team, then standard wheel jail (Please correct me if i'm wrong)\n3. Premium Pulls - Should I just put them all into the random pulls or wait for the rerun of a character I want?\n\nAny comments/ suggestions would be highly appreciated! Thanks.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T13:10:47.447000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1427282423749541928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tips on Pulls as a F2P", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1427285139091882034", "channel_id": "1427282423749541928", "type": 0, "author_id": "1173101039180853258", "author_name": "phanducthinh.com", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello and welcome to the game\n\n1- Yes u need 5 team in the end game d -zone where u farm for very importain resoure that help u lv pass 60. \n2. Yes u right try to get 19 diff awaker so u can build 5 team for d zone then u stuck in wheel jail for the rest of the game.\n\n3. Save all of it for next month anni which have every limited awaker banner so u can plan your stuff, I also newbie like u and save up to 400 already.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T13:21:34.835000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💚", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1427282423749541928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tips on Pulls as a F2P", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1427310079928959069", "channel_id": "1427282423749541928", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@688380814370930815>\nHi f2p here. I don't believe in saving.\nFor point 3, we don't know what anni will have but we guess it will be like first anni which has a rotational banner. It is a banner which changes every day and rotates between all awakers in game twice. But this doesn't have better rates, so you pulling clem now vs you pulling clem during anni is the same thing. It even shares pity.\nWhat does have a different rate is timeless banner, its hard pity is at 60 and there's a 50% chance to get awaker or wheel. It's great when you want both\nFor reference normal limited awaker banner hard pity at 90 pulls and limited wheel banner hard pity at 60 pulls.", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T15:00:41.194000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["688380814370930815"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💚", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1427282423749541928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tips on Pulls as a F2P", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"]}
